Package: otvPlots
Title: Over Time Variable Plots
Version: 0.2.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Rebecca", "Payne", role = "aut"),
    person("Zoey", "Zhu", email = "yixian.zhu@capitalone.com", role = c("aut")),
		person("Yingbo", "Li", email = "yingbo.li@capitalone.com", role = c("aut", "cre")),
		person("Capital One", email = "OpenSourceOffice@capitalone.com", role = "cph"))
Description: This package enables automated visualization of variable 
    distribution and change over time for predictive model building.
    It efficiently computes summary statistics aggreated by time for 
    large datasets, and create plots for variable level monitoring.  
